original: RÖNNHAGEN, Erik Gustaf, Direktör, Norrköping, f Nrkp 13/7 95, gm Lisa Wennerstam. Kont.ch i Algot Holmberg & Söner AB 16—20, disp AB Lantmannafrb i Gävle 21—25, dir f Rönnhagen AB 26—31, vkst dir Hyresgästernas Sparkasse- o Byggn.frn i Nrkp sed. 32, Rest- o Kafé AB Norcopia Nrkp sed. 37. Led tax- o bostadssoc.nmd. Styr.led HSB Riksfrb, HSB Nrkp, AB Borohus, AB Juno-hus, stift Solgårdar o Pensionärshem, Fastigh AB Skeppet, AB Norcopia, Frn Allmännyttiga Kafébolag samt ett 15-tal bostadskoop frn. Frimurare.
translated: RÖNNHAGEN, Erik Gustaf, Director, Norrköping, born in Norrköping on July 13th, 1895, married to Lisa Wennerstam. Financial clerk at Algot Holmberg & Sons AB from 1916 to 1920, manager at AB Lantmannafrb in Gävle from 1921 to 1925, director of Rönnhagen AB from 1926 to 1931, deputy director at Hyresgästernas Sparkasse- and Byggn.frn in Norrköping since 1932, director of Rest- and Kafé AB Norcopia in Norrköping since 1937. Member of the tax- and housing committee. Board member of HSB Riksfrb, HSB Norrköping, AB Borohus, AB Juno-hus, Solgårdar and Pensionärshem Foundation, Fastigh AB Skeppet, AB Norcopia, Allmännyttiga Kafébolag, and about 15 housing cooperatives. Freemason.
